item_description: A beautiful pendant shaped like a crescent moon. Legend says that it was once owned by a powerful mage.
A rare consumable item that restores a player's HP and MP.
An enchanted stone that increases a player's Agility stat.
An ornate and powerful hammer used by blacksmiths to create masterpieces.
A rare and powerful ice-infused arrow used by archers in battle.
An armor made from the scales of a dragon, providing exceptional protection.
A fiery ring that enhances a player's offensive capabilities.
A small, lucky charm that brings good fortune to its owner.
A powerful healing staff used by clerics and other healing classes.
A magical shield that protects a player's MP from being drained.
